      "content": "that's super helpful. for the conclusion, i want to end on a really powerful note. can you write a concluding paragraph that basically says that without these specific redistribution policies, any attempt at racial justice is just performative and won't actually change anything? like, make it clear that redistribution is the only morally legitimate path forward.",
